headline: Majority of Mechanical Contractors Make Digital Fabrication the New Industry Standard, DEWALT® and Dodge Construction Network Study Finds
summary: BOSTON, February 19, 2026--Digital fabrication is now required to win work: 82% of mechanical contractors say owners/GCs demand it, per new Dodge + DEWALT study.
